{"tid":2162290,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"古思堯患直腸癌月底開刀 官准侮辱國旗案押後兼減保釋金","createTime":"2020-08-18T04:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T07:17:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c489226e055976d216de88342a566e7b6cee7f96","tid":2162290,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/NVAQQUN3NNANZIDWTAKMOGJUPE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2FNVAQQUN3NNANZIDWTAKMOGJUPE%2F&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=4d2068c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2FNVAQQUN3NNANZIDWTAKMOGJUPE%2F&h=9a825c06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/NVAQQUN3NNANZIDWTAKMOGJUPE/</a><br />\n<br />\n罹患直腸癌的社運人士古思堯於今年7月，到法院聲援黎智英、李柱銘等15人被控煽惑非法集結一案時，涉舉起一面倒插及塗污的國旗，被控侮辱國旗罪。案件原定下周再訊，惟辯方律師何俊仁今向法庭表示，古將於本月26日接受手術，切除部份肝臟，申請將案押後至11月26日。主任裁判官羅德泉批准申請，並考慮到古的健康狀況急劇轉變，棄保潛逃風險大大降低，將其保釋金由2,000元下調至200元。"},{"pid":"4199671fd2c0bc13849c9a063679942cbfecac61","tid":2162290,"uid":7323,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T04:57:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">喂喂喂，企開啲啦，屌你老母</span>"},{"pid":"55648d723a556257b71ff210f4d91784b4901a63","tid":2162290,"uid":68111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />200蚊係jm9"},{"pid":"2f86e30c018e6ad86a707b949e68bc784991508b","tid":2162290,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55648d723a556257b71ff210f4d91784b4901a63","tid":2162290,"uid":68111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />200蚊係jm9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"法庭果面咁都仍然要有個象徴式保釋條件"},{"pid":"73801